1
00:01:38,080 --> 00:01:38,800
What is it?

2
00:01:38,840 --> 00:01:41,039
You're pacing back and forth. Sit down.

3
00:01:41,240 --> 00:01:42,039
I'd rather not.

4
00:01:42,039 --> 00:01:43,500
I've been sitting all day.

5
00:01:48,960 --> 00:01:50,620
Where exactly did we go wrong?

6
00:01:57,080 --> 00:01:57,880
Well...

7
00:01:59,000 --> 00:02:00,880
Actually, our research data

8
00:02:01,520 --> 00:02:02,160
isn't exactly

9
00:02:02,160 --> 00:02:03,360
completely useless.

10
00:02:04,320 --> 00:02:05,520
A boss from Hong Kong

11
00:02:05,920 --> 00:02:06,920
made me an offer.

12
00:02:07,240 --> 00:02:09,160
Over one million.

13
00:02:09,320 --> 00:02:10,320
Were you tempted?

14
00:02:10,520 --> 00:02:11,650
Did you contact him?

15
00:02:11,720 --> 00:02:12,600
No.

16
00:02:13,040 --> 00:02:14,760
They contacted me.

17
00:02:15,040 --> 00:02:16,170
Just asking around.

18
00:02:16,320 --> 00:02:17,000
Right now,

19
00:02:17,000 --> 00:02:18,360
we can't even afford to eat.

20
00:02:18,360 --> 00:02:20,420
Is it a problem if we take our research

21
00:02:20,520 --> 00:02:21,480
and monetize it a little?

22
00:02:21,480 --> 00:02:22,400
Is there?

23
00:02:22,760 --> 00:02:23,760
I see nothing wrong with it.

24
00:02:23,760 --> 00:02:24,640
You see nothing wrong with it?

25
00:02:24,640 --> 00:02:26,120
How many times have I told you?

26
00:02:26,120 --> 00:02:27,800
We're not just doing this for money.

27
00:02:27,800 --> 00:02:29,120
It's about ideals and ambition.

28
00:02:29,120 --> 00:02:30,720
If we find Buluotuo's Tears,

29
00:02:30,720 --> 00:02:32,650
we'll be archaeological legends.

30
00:02:32,800 --> 00:02:33,760
Well, we have to live

31
00:02:33,760 --> 00:02:35,120
until that day comes.

32
00:02:35,120 --> 00:02:35,960
Why wouldn't we?

33
00:02:35,960 --> 00:02:36,880
We are young.

34
00:02:36,880 --> 00:02:37,600
Look at you.

35
00:02:37,760 --> 00:02:38,560
Talking about...

36
00:02:38,560 --> 00:02:39,890
The Legend of Buluotuo,

37
00:02:39,960 --> 00:02:41,040
Buluotuo's Tears.

38
00:02:41,320 --> 00:02:42,440
I think that stuff

39
00:02:42,440 --> 00:02:43,600
is just your wishful thinking.

40
00:02:43,600 --> 00:02:44,720
You just imagined it.

41
00:02:44,720 --> 00:02:45,440
All day long,

42
00:02:45,440 --> 00:02:46,880
ideals, ideals, ideals.

43
00:02:47,200 --> 00:02:48,760
What are ideals worth?

44
00:02:49,400 --> 00:02:50,720
Can ideals buy us food?

45
00:02:51,160 --> 00:02:52,400
You really have no conscience.

46
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:53,160
We talked about this before.

47
00:02:53,160 --> 00:02:54,280
Who am I doing this for?

48
00:02:54,280 --> 00:02:55,240
It's for the two of us.

49
00:02:55,240 --> 00:02:56,240
Including you.

50
00:02:56,280 --> 00:02:57,680
Let me be clear right now.

51
00:02:57,840 --> 00:02:58,900
If you dare do this,

52
00:02:59,000 --> 00:02:59,760
even though you're my own brother,

53
00:02:59,760 --> 00:03:00,600
I will send you to prison.

54
00:03:00,600 --> 00:03:01,320
Try me.

55
00:03:02,360 --> 00:03:03,120
You said that.

56
00:03:03,120 --> 00:03:03,760
Yes.

57
00:03:04,360 --> 00:03:05,720
Save your energy.

58
00:03:06,040 --> 00:03:07,300
I'm leaving right now.

59
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:09,120
I won't live like this

60
00:03:09,120 --> 00:03:09,920
for one more minute.

61
00:03:09,920 --> 00:03:11,000
I refuse.

62
00:03:13,320 --> 00:03:14,120
Come back.

63
00:03:28,840 --> 00:03:29,640
I'm sorry.

64
00:03:30,560 --> 00:03:31,620
Please forgive me.

65
00:03:31,680 --> 00:03:32,680
Please forgive me too.

66
00:03:32,680 --> 00:03:33,410
Don't be mad.

67
00:03:33,520 --> 00:03:34,920
I didn't mean what I said.

68
00:03:46,520 --> 00:03:47,600
What are you doing?

69
00:03:48,200 --> 00:03:49,200
You can't.

70
00:03:49,280 --> 00:03:50,480
You can't take it away.

71
00:03:50,480 --> 00:03:51,880
They are still inside.

72
00:03:52,000 --> 00:03:53,640
They will be lost forever.

73
00:03:54,000 --> 00:03:55,400
It was mine to begin with.

74
00:03:57,360 --> 00:03:58,760
It doesn't belong to you.

75
00:04:00,720 --> 00:04:02,480
You are my own brother.

76
00:04:05,040 --> 00:04:06,360
It has nothing to do with me.

77
00:04:06,360 --> 00:04:07,440
You are my own brother.

78
00:04:07,440 --> 00:04:08,970
It has nothing to do with me.

79
00:04:14,760 --> 00:04:15,400
I'm sorry.

80
00:04:15,560 --> 00:04:17,880
You'll get everyone killed.

81
00:04:19,360 --> 00:04:21,560
They are still inside.

82
00:04:23,240 --> 00:04:24,920
I failed all of you.

83
00:04:27,840 --> 00:04:29,240
I don't feel like

84
00:04:37,280 --> 00:04:38,400
I don't feel like

85
00:04:38,640 --> 00:04:40,080
you're sorry at all.

86
00:04:40,320 --> 00:04:40,840
Speak.

87
00:04:40,920 --> 00:04:41,880
What do you want to say?

88
00:04:41,880 --> 00:04:42,720
Do you know

89
00:04:43,080 --> 00:04:44,040
this old man

90
00:04:44,320 --> 00:04:45,640
is so stingy?

91
00:04:46,000 --> 00:04:46,880
Growing up,

92
00:04:46,880 --> 00:04:48,280
I never had a Western meal.

93
00:04:48,280 --> 00:04:50,240
He made me eat big pot stew every day.

94
00:04:50,240 --> 00:04:51,120
Why did I do that?

95
00:04:51,120 --> 00:04:52,450
It was for your own good.

96
00:04:52,520 --> 00:04:53,960
I was afraid you'd go astray

97
00:04:53,960 --> 00:04:56,020
and become someone like Black Snake.

98
00:04:56,120 --> 00:04:57,440
Should I thank you for that?

99
00:04:57,440 --> 00:04:58,900
Stop arguing, both of you.

100
00:04:59,040 --> 00:04:59,720
Liu Yu.

101
00:04:59,920 --> 00:05:01,320
Your parents' goal was to find Buluotuo's Tear.

102
00:05:01,320 --> 00:05:02,920
That's why they went missing

103
00:05:02,920 --> 00:05:03,880
while looking for

104
00:05:03,880 --> 00:05:05,560
the Bronze Frog.

105
00:05:05,680 --> 00:05:07,120
Finding Buluotuo's Tear

106
00:05:07,240 --> 00:05:09,370
is also a journey to find your parents.

107
00:05:09,560 --> 00:05:10,820
You and Professor Wei,

108
00:05:11,280 --> 00:05:13,120
you share the same goal.

109
00:05:15,880 --> 00:05:16,740
Professor Wei,

110
00:05:17,120 --> 00:05:19,080
you can't blame this entirely on Liu Yu.

111
00:05:19,080 --> 00:05:19,880
Your brother,

112
00:05:21,880 --> 00:05:23,280
Black Snake's betrayal

113
00:05:23,880 --> 00:05:25,320
has made you a bit sensitive.

114
00:05:25,320 --> 00:05:26,580
You're overreacting.

115
00:05:26,880 --> 00:05:28,080
Shake hands, come on.

116
00:05:28,240 --> 00:05:29,400
We have work to do.

117
00:05:31,360 --> 00:05:32,820
I'll be the bigger person.

118
00:05:33,280 --> 00:05:34,280
Let's make peace.

119
00:05:41,760 --> 00:05:42,320
Fine.

120
00:05:42,960 --> 00:05:44,820
Since you admitted your mistake.

121
00:05:56,440 --> 00:05:58,000
Mom, Dad.

122
00:05:58,200 --> 00:05:59,920
I will find Buluotuo's Tear

123
00:06:00,520 --> 00:06:01,840
and bring you both back.
